OL,6,FThe Stormont Assembly has been urged
OL,7,Fto "bloody well get on" and fix issues
OL,8,Fexposed by the UK Covid-19 Inquiry.
OL,10,FBrenda Campbell KC, acting for
OL,11,FBereaved Families for Justice NI, said
OL,12,Fthe three weeks of hearings held in
OL,13,FBelfast had been "very difficult" for
OL,14,Fthe bereaved.
OL,16,FMaking her closing submissions on
OL,17,FThursday, Ms Campbell said the last
OL,18,Fthree weeks have been "littered with
OL,19,Foversights, omissions and feelings".
